title: Figurine of a Cat
description:
Statuette of a cat sitting on its haunches, front legs erect. Ears are pierced with earring in right ear. Earring is round hoop with tapered ends which cross each other. Two tang in base. 

Condition: Fair; tip of tail and hind legs are broken off; large hole in chest.
dimensions: Height (without tang) 2 7/16 x 7/8 x 1 5/8 in. (6.2 x 2.2 x 4.1 cm)
